{
  "stem": "24346.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And his sons-- meaning my cousins, he introduced as his helpers, also bricklayers, and they did work in the building department.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And since my brother was a watchmaker-- who needed watches?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't need watches.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he worked with my uncle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "However, there came a time when the Germans got wise-- like, you have the stories now going on with the gold to Switzerland-- that they opened up Rumkowski [NON-ENGLISH]-- in Yiddish, it's called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What is the [NON-ENGLISH]?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was like a [NON-ENGLISH], where you trade things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So everybody could bring in their gold and they would give them money-- not what is on the market, but, like, a black market price so they could afford to buy extra food.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So my brother's a watchmaker, and knowingly in gold, could test the gold, because the Germans gave them all these chemicals that needed-- remember, he used to scratch it, put on some of the stuff-- I don't remember what it's called-- but it was a chemical and could tell whether it was gold.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he got a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So at least-- because he used to carry, there, two pails of cement.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I want you to know, cement is very heavy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I tried that, you know, a few times, to help to make a few bucks extra, when I had a chance.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It nearly pulled my arms off my socket pits.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's how heavy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he worked that eight, nine, or ten hours a day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So my mother was relieved when he got the shop in the [NON-ENGLISH] as testing gold or fixing watches, repair watches for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because, eventually, this gold was not for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
